    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>PRIVILEGIUM COMITISSE MATILDIS NON SIGILATO ET NON TESTATO ET SINE TESTIBUS.
                        In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. <rs key="#Breve/memoratorium">Brevis
                            recordationis</rs> pro futuris temporibus ad memoriam retinendam. Noscat
                        universalis ecclesia quod ego <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/2157"
                            >Ubaldus</persName> quamvis indignus <orgName
                            key="#Mother_churches #Bishops #Breve/memoratorium #Decima #Churches #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1426"><placeName key="#Mother_churches"
                                ref="#places/275">Mantuane</placeName> tamen <rs
                                key="#Mother_churches">ecclesie</rs></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> dictus, <rs key="#Intercessory">rogatu et
                            peticione</rs> domine <persName key="#Countess #marriage #Intercessory"
                            ref="#people/125">Matildis</persName> venerabilis <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitisse</rs>, <rs key="#Public_rituals">cum anulo aureo
                            investivi</rs>
                        <persName key="#marriage" ref="#people/2159">Welfonem</persName> suum <rs
                            key="#marriage">virum</rs> de omnibus rebus sancte Mantuane ecclesie que
                            <persName key="#Marquis/duke #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi"
                            ref="#people/1">Bonifacio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">ma[r]chio</rs> habuit et tenuit in die mortis sue,
                        excepto quod ipsa cometissa Matilda olim ecclesie dimiserat: <rs
                            key="#Decima">decimas</rs> silicet de <placeName key="#Decima"
                            ref="#places/2489">Campitello</placeName>, et omnes <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesias</rs> eiusdem episcopatus cum omnibus bonis suis; et alia <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">precariam</rs> in Campitello in
                        loco qui dicitur <placeName key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi"
                            ref="#places/2489">Cuvulo</placeName>, quam fecit marchio cum <persName
                            key="#Bishops #Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Mansi" ref="#people/2158"
                            >Nulfo</persName> episcopo Mantuano, que continet ducentos triginta et
                        tres <rs key="#Mansi">mansos</rs>, habentes <rs key="#Size">per unumquemque
                            mansum iugera decem</rs>; et decimas de <placeName key="#Decima"
                            ref="#places/2915">Gothi</placeName>, de <placeName key="#Decima"
                            ref="#places/2916">Cerlungo</placeName>, de <placeName key="#Decima"
                            ref="#places/2917">Vulta</placeName>, de <placeName key="#Decima"
                            ref="#places/2918">Capriana</placeName>, de <placeName key="#Decima"
                            ref="#places/2919">Gosenaco</placeName>, de <placeName key="#Decima"
                            ref="#places/2920">Beneficio</placeName>, de <placeName key="#Decima"
                            ref="#places/2921">Bigarello</placeName> sibi dedimus et cetera.
                        Notificavimus eidem domine comitisse in presencia domini <persName
                            key="#Breve/memoratorium #Witness #Bishops" ref="#people/2160"
                            >Benedicti</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Bishops" ref="#places/38">Mutinensis</placeName> episcopi
                        et <persName key="#Breve/memoratorium #Witness #childOf"><name
                                ref="Maginfredus/f. Roberti">Manfredi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>
                        <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Robertus">Roberti</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Breve/memoratorium #Witness #Judge"><name
                                ref="Aldricus/iudex">Alderici</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> et aliorum multorum sepissime, quod
                        supradictus marchio tenebat <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2064"><rs
                                key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> de <placeName key="#Curtes"
                                >Vuarzatico</placeName></geogName> quam <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/123">Athelardus</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Bishops" ref="#places/59">Veronensis</placeName> episcopus
                        per scriptum olim ecclesie dederat; et <rs key="#Monasteries">abaciam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/2056">Sancti
                            Cassiani</orgName> a paganis olim devastatam, quam <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/118">Lodoicus</persName> pie memorie
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> similiter per scriptum et per
                        choerencias ecclesie dederat; et <geogName key="#Forests"
                            ref="#estates/2065"><rs key="#Forests">silvas</rs> de iuxta
                            Mencium</geogName>; et <geogName key="#Forests #Islands"
                            ref="#estates/2066">silvas <rs key="#Islands">insule</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Forests #Islands" ref="#places/2400">Sancti
                                Benedicti</placeName></geogName>; et omnes <rs>homines</rs> super
                        terram ecclesie in civitate rexidentes; et multa alia que marchio Nulfo
                        episcopo Mantuano, qui me clericum fecit, per vim abstullerat, sicul in
                        literis ab eodem ad mernoriam factis continetur. Diximus eciam eidem domine
                        de curte Lothuli, quam Meltruda uxor Riprandi similiter per cartam ecclesie
                        nostre dedit; et curtem Asili, excepto illo quod Bernardus de Burbasio per
                        beneficium habuit, quam quidam Albericus per scriptum ecclesie dedit; et
                        teras et silvas et piscariam que iacent inter Iaram et Larionem; et viam
                        Focariciam, et fossam Fanti, et Scorçariolum iuxta Savinulam; et curtem de
                        Rivoverso, et curtem de Runcorolandi, cum silvis et venacionibus et
                        piscariis quam Arnulfus rex ecclesie dedit per scriptum; et multa per
                        comitatum in curtibus et in silvis et in arimania in serta; et curtem de
                        Corniliano cum tota silva iuxta Castellun Novum, quam abstulit <persName
                            key="#Bishops" ref="#people/2162">Marciano</persName> Mantuano episcopo,
                        qui me archidiaconum ordinavit, nobis scientibus, presentibus et videntibus;
                        et insulam Carariam quam <persName key="#Viscount"><name
                                ref="Dodo/vicecomes">Dodo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomes</rs> per libellum tenuit, et decem solidos
                        annualiter ex ea pro pensione episcopo solvebat; et medietatem fossati
                        Lotholi; et omnes homines qui extra civitatem in burgo tunc temporis erant,
                        tempore domni Marciani episcopi ad suum servicium invasit, qui supra terram
                        ecclesie similiter resident, et qui postea venerunt super eandem terram et
                        cotidie veniunt, cotidie invaduntur; quos omnes <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">preceptario iure multorum imperatorum</rs>
                        ecclesia sine omni impedimento habere et tenere debet. Investivimus enim
                        ducem Welfonem sicut diximus anno Domini, etcetera. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
